HEADWORD: bobbysoxer
<hw>bob"by*sox`er</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an adolescent girl wearing
bobby socks (common in the 1940s); -- sometimes used for any adolescent
girl, especially one following the latest youthful fashion .</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> bobbysocker.</syn>⟦br⟧
